    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently struggles to start and exhibits a noticeable knock, while the transmission slips during gear changes. Externally, the body shows several large dents, significant paint oxidation, and visible rust spots on the wheel wells. The interior has seen heavy use, with multiple tears in the upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and several non-functional electronic components, including the radio and climate control. This car is best suited for a dedicated project restorer or as a source for spare parts.",
