    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2020 sedan in good condition. The exterior has minor cosmetic scratches and small dings from regular use. The interior is well-maintained with light wear on the seats and carpet. The engine and all mechanical components are in good working order.",
      "price": 34500.0,
